body_html:
I can reproduce this on MacOS 10.13, python 3.6.3.

$ python -V
Python 3.6.3 :: Anaconda, Inc.

$ pip install tensorflow tensorboard

$ pip freeze|grep tensor
tensorboard==1.0.0a6
tensorflow==1.4.1
tensorflow-tensorboard==0.4.0rc3

@jhseu what's your setup?

I can reproduce this on MacOS 10.13, python 3.6.3.

```
$ python -V
Python 3.6.3 :: Anaconda, Inc.

$ pip install tensorflow tensorboard

$ pip freeze|grep tensor
tensorboard==1.0.0a6
tensorflow==1.4.1
tensorflow-tensorboard==0.4.0rc3
```

@jhseu what's your setup?
